metadata.name: Eternity
metadata.description:
Even though the eyes are not as beautiful as the morning star, every woman can have
dew eyes. Shady. Cool. It's not easy to get emotional. Dealing with behavior
surroundings wisely. He always has a good attitude. His words
not a knife that stabs. His words are burning embers
passion in the chest. No wasted words left his lips. women will become creatures of eternal beauty, don't change that.

Detail artwork : 2500 x 3000 px 300 DPi

2022
